<concept id="about">
  <title>About</title>
  <shortdesc>The DITA Open Toolkit, or DITA-OT for short, is a set of Java-based, open source tools
    that provide processing for DITA maps and topic content.</shortdesc>
  <conbody>
    <p>You can download the OT and install it for free on your computer to get started with
      topic-based writing and publishing.</p>
